---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | 5.Y"
  description="5.Y Terms & Conditions - Please read these terms carefully before using our website and services."
  canonicalUrl="https://www.five-whys.com/terms"
  activeNav=""
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="pt-16 px-8 pb-8 text-center bg-bg-secondary border-b border-border-theme">
      <h1 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-medium tracking-[-0.02em] mb-4">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg">Please read these terms carefully before using our website and services.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-8 pt-12 pb-20">
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">Welcome to the official website of 5Y Holdings Pte. Ltd. (5.Y). By accessing or using this site, you agree to the terms outlined below.</p>

      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-medium text-text-primary mt-10 mb-4">The Basics</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">The content provided on this website is intended for general informational purposes and may be modified at any time without prior notice. While we aim to ensure the accuracy of our content, we cannot guarantee that the site will always be error-free or uninterrupted. These Terms &amp; Conditions (T&amp;Cs) only apply to this website. 5.Y Products and Services are governed with separate T&amp;Cs.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Intellectual Property</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">Some of the materials, including text, images, and branding, are the exclusive property of 5.Y. You may not copy, reproduce, modify, or distribute any content without prior written consent from 5.Y.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Cookies and Analytics</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">This website uses cookies and tracking technologies to improve functionality and analyze visitor behavior. By using this site, you consent to the use of cookies. For more details, please review our <a href="/privacy" class="text-accent underline">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Third-Party Links</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">This website may include links to external websites for your convenience. 5.Y is not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of these third-party websites.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">5.Y is not liable for any damages arising from the use of this website, including errors, omissions, or reliance on third-party links.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Governing Law</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">These terms are governed by the laws of Singapore, the jurisdiction in which 5.Y operates.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-6 mb-3">Policy Updates</h3>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8] mb-6">We may update these Terms &amp; Conditions periodically. Continued use of this website implies acceptance of the latest terms.</p>

      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-[1.8]">For any inquiries or concerns regarding these Terms &amp; Conditions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@five-whys.com" class="text-accent underline">info@five-whys.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
